The paper proposes a new graph neural network model for predicting quantum mechanical properties of molecules. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model also involves using embeddings and message passing, which are common techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper presents experimental results and comparisons with previous models, which is typical of papers in the subfield of scientific computing (cs.SI).
